        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Character certificate&#8212; Samuel C. Hirams.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>State of Louisiana</placeName></p>

<p><placeName>Parish of La Fayette</placeName></p>
<p>This is to Certify that <persName>Samuel C. Hirams</persName> (the <persName>bearer </persName>of this) is a
<persName>man of respect</persName> and Esteem among us, that he is qualifyed for 
buisness of any kind, having receaved a liberal education, and do not
hesitate to say that he is a man in whoom publick confidence can be
placed.</p>

<p>Given under my hand and seal This <date when="1824-12-20">20th day of Dec. 1824.</date></p>

<p><persName>John Greig<lb/>
Clk and J. P. for the Parish and State</persName> afd.</p>

        </div1>
